SUMMARY:The Crooked Shoes at The Block
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to kick off the outdoor concert season in Petaluma with a night of moody\, high-energy rock! Crooked Shoes is taking the stage at The Block on Saturday\, March 21st\, and this is one performance you won’t want to miss. Crooked Shoes isn’t just “background music.” Their original music is known for its raw\, honest songwriting and infectious hooks that is as danceable as it is dark. Expect covers to be deep cuts from the likes of Queens of the Stone Age\, The Tragically Hip and Incubus as well as 90s alternative rock. \nCrooked Shoes: Katie Schuch\, Dean Cupp\, Mitch Thomas\, Alex Fabian Davis\, Faith Waligora and Tim Gahagan
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-crooked-shoes-at-the-block/
LOCATION:The Block Petaluma\, 20 Grey Street\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
