SUMMARY:Comedian Monica Piper
DESCRIPTION:The Laugh Cellar presents:\nHeadliner Monica Piper in the Historic Wine Tool Museum at Buena Vista Winery \nLos Angeles-based headliner comedian Monica Piper is an Emmy and Golden Globe Award-winning comedy writer\, actor\, and comedian. She has written for hit sitcoms including Roseanne and Mad About You\, and served as head writer and producer of the #1 children’s animated series\, Rugrats. A standout performer\, Monica starred in her own Showtime Network special\, No\, Monica\, Just You\, and was nominated by the American Comedy Awards as one of the top five female comedians in the country. \nComplimentary parking on-site\n21+ Indoor event\, theater style seating\nDoors 6:00pm \nAVAILABLE FOR PURCHASE:\nA delicious selection of wine and sparkling wine by the bottle and glass\nOakville Cheese & Charcuterie trays
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/comedian-monica-piper/
LOCATION:Buena Vista Winery\, 18000 Old Winery Rd\, Sonoma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Comedy
