SUMMARY:SOLD OUT -Cloverdale Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:The Cloverdale Cabaret was born at the Cloverdale Citrus Fair as a bold\, scrappy passion project—our fledgling production stepping into a new chapter\, and our first without longtime director Ashlyn at the helm (missed dearly). \nWhat began as a spark of after-hours mischief has grown into an intimate cabaret-in-concert that showcases the heart of our company: some of the incredible singers and dancers you’ve loved in past productions\, reunited in a more up-close\, electric setting. \nThis cabaret leans decidedly more adult than our Citrus Fair dinner show—cheekier\, sultrier\, and a little dangerous—while still celebrating the theatricality\, live vocals\, and ensemble magic that define us. It’s a chance to see familiar performers in a new light\, telling stories through big songs\, bold choreography\, and unapologetic flair\, all in the heart of our beloved town.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/cloverdale-cabaret-3/
LOCATION:Cloverdale Performing Arts Center\, 209 N. Cloverdale Blvd.\, Cloverdale\, CA
CATEGORIES:Theater
GEO:38.8066;-123.018
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Cloverdale Performing Arts Center 209 N. Cloverdale Blvd. Cloverdale CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=209 N. Cloverdale Blvd.:geo:-123.018,38.8066
END:VEVENT
