SUMMARY:The Fargo Brothers at The California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Soaring harmonies\, rootsy grooves\, and high-energy tributes\, The Fargo Brothers deliver nonstop rock\, blues & Americana.\nThe Fargo Brothers are an award-winning rock\, blues\, and Americana band celebrated for their soaring vocal harmonies and tight\, electrifying ensemble playing. Their high-energy shows feature crowd-pleasing medley tributes to legends like The Beatles\, Rolling Stones\, Tom Petty\, ZZ Top\, Stevie Ray Vaughan\, John Hiatt\, and Delbert McClinton.\nBlending these classics seamlessly with a deep catalog of original songs\, The Fargo Brothers deliver a nonstop\, fun-filled performance that spans genres and generations\, bringing the stage to life from the first note to the last. \nBUY TICKETS IN ADVANCE AND SAVE!\nZONE A: $25\nZONE B: $20\nZONE C: $15 \nTickets at the door: $25 (Zone C only) \nShowtime 7:30pm\, doors open 6:30pm\nOur kitchen is open and serving our All New Menu from the time doors open until end of intermission.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-fargo-brothers-at-the-california-theatre/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Fargo-Brothers.jpg
