SUMMARY:MaMuse at The Sebastopol Community Cultural Center
DESCRIPTION:Welcome the return of the light with MaMuse! Born from a moment of creative alchemy in Northern California\, MaMuse’s music is rooted in the elements – soil and rivers\, ash and fire – and carried by songs that have become communal anthems around the world. From campfires and concert halls to weddings\, funerals\, and birthings\, their music invites connection\, reflection\, and renewal. Join us for a soulful evening of song and community as we gather to mark the Spring Equinox together.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/mamuse-at-the-sebastopol-community-cultural-center/
LOCATION:Sebastopol Community Cultural Center\, 390 Morris St\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
