SUMMARY:Sol Horizon at The Vintage Space
DESCRIPTION:Sol Horizon has been Sonoma County’s premier reggae band for the past 25 years. The band was voted “Best Band” in the North Bay Bohemian’s “Best of the North Bay” Reader’s Picks in 2022 and 2023\, as well as “Best Reggae Band” in the North Bay 8 times\, including the last 4 years in a row and 7 of the previous 8 years. The band is renowned for its energetic live performances and powerful lyrical content\, which focuses on themes of peace\, positivity\, community\, sustainability\, and the revitalizing power of nature. The band members are deeply rooted in and nurtured by their dynamic local community\, with strong ties to the arts and culture of Sonoma County\, as well as its delicate natural splendor. \nSol Horizon is also Northern California’s premier Bob Marley tribute band\, paying tribute to the global voice of reggae music\, celebrating the life and legacy of Bob Marley by performing some of Bob Marley’s greatest music.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sol-horizon-at-the-vintage-space/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
