SUMMARY:School of Rock Santa Rosa – Season 22
DESCRIPTION:ABOUT: \nSchool of Rock Santa Rosa – Season 22 Midseason Shows \nJoin us for the Season 22 Midseason Shows featuring the talented students of School of Rock Santa Rosa! These performances showcase our Performance Program\, Rock 101\, and Adult bands halfway through the season as they bring their hard work from the rehearsal room to the stage. \nStudents will perform a high-energy mix of rock classics and modern favorites\, demonstrating the progress they’ve made through School of Rock’s performance-based music education program. From first-time performers to seasoned student musicians\, these shows highlight teamwork\, confidence\, and the joy of live music. \nFamily\, friends\, and music lovers of all ages are encouraged to attend and support these incredible young (and adult!) rockers. Come early\, stay late\, and enjoy a full day of live music while cheering on our School of Rock community.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/school-of-rock-santa-rosa-season-22/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
